const Roadmap = () => { return (

Roadmap

Edition 1 : Create 1,500 Unique, Cute, and Collectible Hippo Family. Hippos Male are created!

Marketplace Integration – Solanart, DigitalEyes, Magic Eden Will be #1 priority at launch, should happen soon after minting.

Limited Edition NFTs Drops Associated Limited Edition NFTs will be minted at the programmer’s discretion and given away. Collect more Hippos to have a higher chance to get one. Competitions will also be held for these limited edited NFTs.

Edition 2 : Create 1,500 Unique, Cute, and Collectible Hippo Family. Hippos Female are created!

Hippo Wedding - You will be able to submit 2 NFTs (Male and Female) and you will get a new cute Hippos Baby NFTs in your family.

) } export default Roadmap;
